            "title": "Diet Segregation between Sexes by a Gregarious Greater Antillean Bat, Phyllonycteris poeyi (Chiroptera: Phyllostomidae)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Margarita",
