            "title": "Cranial Morphology of the Flat-Headed Bat Myotis planiceps (Chiroptera: Vespertilionidae) in the Context of American Myotis",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Sandra M.",
