            "title": "Reproductive Stages and Ovarian Histophysiology in Artibeus planirostris (Chiroptera: Phyllostomidae) in the Dry and Rainy Months in a Municipality of the Mesoregion of the Mata Pernambucana, Northeastern Brazil",
            "creators": [
                {
